ent-ActionPlasmamanDash = Plasma Dash
    .desc = Vent plasma from your body to launch yourself a short distance forward. Only works in space - range scales with your breath saturation, and costs some of it.

plasmaman-dash-no-vacuum = There's too much atmosphere here for the dash to push off anything.
plasmaman-dash-no-breath = You don't have enough plasma in your system to vent.
